title: Radiohead - The National Anthem (Live at South Park, Oxford, 2001)

media:group.media:title: Radiohead - The National Anthem (Live at South Park, Oxford, 2001)
media:group.media:description:
Recorded live at South Park, Oxford on 7th July 2001. 

The T-shirts at this show used a design specially gifted to us by the more famous South Park namesake. We are re-issuing them for a limited time - get yours HERE: https://smarturl.it/w.a.s.t.e
Like everything from the original show, all proceeds will go to a deserved cause and this time it will be: https://www.safepassage.org.uk

Browse through the KID A MNESIA exhibition and visit the gift shop: https://kida-mnesia.com
KID A MNESIA is out now: https://radiohead.ffm.to/kid-a-mnesia
